            </rs>.</p>
               <p>[<rs id="t18111204-1-verdict6" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18111204-1-verdict6" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18111204-1-verdict6" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               The prisoner was recommended to mercy by the prosecutor on account that he believed the prisoner's father sent the property back
            </rs>.]</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. justice Grose.</p>
